quran[7]{c,v,t,f}:
  74,1,"O you (Muhammad صلى الله عليه وسلم) enveloped in garments!"
  74,2,"Arise and warn!"
  74,3,"And magnify your Lord (Allâh)!"
  74,4,"And purify your garments!"
  74,5,"And keep away from Ar-Rujz (the idols)!"
  74,6,"And give not a thing in order to have more (or consider not your deeds of obedience to Allâh as a favour to Him)."
  74,7,"And be patient for the sake of your Lord (i.e. perform your duty to Allâh)!"
  74,8,"Then, when the Trumpet is sounded (i.e. the second blowing of the horn)."
  74,9,"Truly, that Day will be a Hard Day -"
  74,10,"Far from easy for the disbelievers."